data.description: You want a small farm or just a piece of paradise this one is for you.  4 sided brick ranch home with 4 bedrooms and 3 bath all sitting on almost 14 acres.  Side entry garage overlooking flat beautiful pasture land.  With this open concept with split bedroom setup.  Walk into the spacious living room and heat up with the fireplace.   Open to kitchen area.  Dining room for more eating room with all those dinners you are going to host now.  From the dining room opens through the french doors to the back deck.  Back inside with spacious kitchen overlooking the living room.  Need that office space, check this one off the list of must haves.  Two large bedrooms on one side of the house with 2 full baths.  Now to the other side with the other 2 bedrooms and another full bath, large laundry room and large 2nd pantry.  This home checks off most of the boxes of all of the extras you want inside and out.    New roof, HVAC, Handrails on porch Septic pumped and much more.
